sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Submit member email
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/workspaces/{id}/members
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace
    DB-->>API: Workspace found
    API->>DB: Find user by email

    alt User exists
        DB-->>API: User found
        API->>DB: Add user to workspace members
        DB-->>API: Membership saved
        API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + member payload
        Frontend-->>Owner: Refresh workspace members list
    else Unknown user
        DB-->>API: No user found
        API-->>Frontend: 404 Not Found
        Frontend-->>Owner: Display error message
    end
